.TH "prayertime-cli" "1" "Mar 2026" "prayertime-cli" ""

.SH NAME
prayertime-cli - CLI-first, agent-native Islamic prayer times tool


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBprayertime-cli [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
CLI-first, agent-native Islamic prayer times tool.

.PP
Contract:
  - Structured payloads go to stdout.
  - Human-readable errors and suggestions go to stderr.
  - With --output json, errors are emitted as JSON on stdout.

.PP
Global output modes:
  - --output text prints human-readable output.
  - --output json prints structured JSON.
  - --output value is reserved for commands that expose --field selectors.
  - --json is a shortcut for --output json.

.PP
Exit codes:
  - 0 success
  - 1 internal failure
  - 2 usage error
  - 3 not found or ambiguous input
  - 4 network or upstream timeout
  - 5 reserved conflict/state error


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for prayertime-cli

.PP
\fB--json\fP[=false]
	Shortcut for --output json

.PP
\fB--output\fP="text"
	Output mode: text, json, or value


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBprayertime-cli-locations(1)\fP, \fBprayertime-cli-times(1)\fP, \fBprayertime-cli-version(1)\fP
